<i>noun</i>: 유혹적 [유혹쩍], 유인 [유인] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>유혹적 [유혹쩍]</dt><br>
<dd>1. enticing; luring</dd><br>
<dd>마음이나 정신을 빼앗는 성질의 것.</dd><br>
<dd>Something that takes away one's mind or attention.</dd><br>
<dd>2. seductive; tempting</dd><br>
<dd>성적으로 이성에게 끌리는 것.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being attracted sexually to someone of the opposite sex.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>유인 [유인]</dt><br>
<dd>luring; seduction</dd><br>
<dd>관심이나 흥미를 일으켜 꾀어냄.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of attracting someone by provoking his/her interest or curiosity.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>